## Ignore Visual Studio / Rider temp files
.vs/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo
*.userprefs

## Build outputs
bin/
obj/
out/
publish/
*.dll
*.pdb
*.exe
*.log

## dotnet
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/
*.nupkg

## Environment / secrets
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.Local.json
.env
.env.*
*.pfx
*.pem
secrets/

## SQLite dev DB
*.db
*.db-*
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-journal

## Azure
.azure/
*.azurePubxml

## Editors
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp

## Node (in case a frontend workspace is added later)
node_modules/
dist/

## iOS
ios/NimShare.xcodeproj/
ios/build/
ios/DerivedData/
ios/*.xcworkspace/
ios/**/*.xcuserdatad/
# Also ignore the two "Browse [conflicted]"-style Finder merge backups
# that occasionally show up under Views/
**/*[conflicted]*.cshtml
**/*[conflicted 2]*.cshtml
